## 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW

Build a complete, production-ready **Flutter mobile application** called **JTC Repair Lab**.

- **App Name:** JTC Repair Lab
- **Platform:** Android (primary), iOS (secondary)
- **Backend:** Zero server. 100% offline. All data stored locally on device.
- **Target Users:** Mobile phone repair shop staff (Usman & Saad)
- **Language:** English UI, Urdu-friendly data entry support (Unicode safe)

