## 4. DATA MODELS

### 4.1 RepairJob (Hive Box: `"repair_jobs"`)

```dart
@HiveType(typeId: 0)
class RepairJob extends HiveObject {
  @HiveField(0)  String id;               // UUID v4
  @HiveField(1)  String customerName;
  @HiveField(2)  String customerPhone;    // e.g. 03001234567
  @HiveField(3)  String customerCNIC;     // e.g. 35201-1234567-1
  @HiveField(4)  String mobileModel;     // Device brand/model
  @HiveField(5)  String issueDescription; // Free text + selected tags
  @HiveField(6)  double repairPrice;
  @HiveField(7)  String estimatedTime;   // e.g. "2 Hours", "Tomorrow 5pm"
  @HiveField(8)  String? imagePath;      // Local file path to device photo
  @HiveField(9)  DateTime receivedAt;
  @HiveField(10) DateTime? completedAt;
  @HiveField(11) String status;          // "pending" | "done" | "issue_found"
  @HiveField(12) String? extraIssueNote; // If technician finds more problems
  @HiveField(13) List<String> issueTags; // Quick-select tags used
}
```

### 4.2 BorrowItem (Hive Box: `"borrow_items"`)

