## 15. ERROR HANDLING

- All Hive operations wrapped in try/catch
- Permission denied → show a dialog explaining what permission is needed and why
- Bluetooth not available → show info snackbar, disable print button gracefully
- WhatsApp not installed → show snackbar: *"WhatsApp is not installed on this device"*
- Image pick cancelled → do nothing silently
- Empty form submission → highlight required fields with red border + error text

