## 16. PERFORMANCE REQUIREMENTS

- App cold launch < 2 seconds on mid-range Android (Snapdragon 660+)
- Hive read/write must be async, never block the UI thread
- Images must be stored as compressed JPEG (quality 70%) to save space
- Max image size: 800x800px (downscale before saving)
- Lazy load job cards in list using `ListView.builder`
- Use `const` constructors everywhere possible

